column8: Mostly sunny. Winds north to northwesterly 20 to 25 km/h becoming light in the morning then becoming northerly 15 to 20 km/h in the late evening.

Partly cloudy. Slight (30%) chance of a shower, most likely in the late afternoon and evening. Winds northerly 20 to 25 km/h tending northwesterly 20 to 30 km/h before dawn then becoming light in the evening.

Partly cloudy. Medium (60%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and evening. The chance of a thunderstorm in the afternoon and evening. Winds south to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h tending northwest to southwesterly during the day then becoming light during the afternoon.

Partly cloudy. High (70%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and evening. The chance of a thunderstorm in the afternoon and evening. Winds northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h tending north to northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning then tending east to northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h during the evening.
Cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers. Winds north to northwesterly 20 to 30 km/h shifting south to southeasterly 20 to 25 km/h during the day.
Cloudy. Medium (40%) chance of showers. Winds west to southwesterly 25 to 35 km/h turning south to southeasterly 30 to 35 km/h during the morning.
Cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of showers. Winds north to northeasterly 30 to 35 km/h turning easterly 20 to 25 km/h later.
